reviewes.review_text: Beatrice is EXCELLENT! Days prior to my event, a baker was no longer able to fulfill my custom treat orders. Searching for another alternative, I revisited Beatrice's Etsy store. When I explained my unfortunate situation, she saw a need and found a way to assist by taking my order and ensuring my items arrived in time for my event. That's truly commendable of her because she had every right not to. Surely, she was a blessing! The treat toppers and sprinkles were beautiful additions to our celebration!! Thank you again Beatrice!
